Neocyberpunks 897 BC (after the Collision)
Moments in the course of events are captured in the distant future after the Collision, where millions of beings disappeared in the blink of an eye.

Years later great civilizations rise thanks to advances in biotechnology and extradimensional jumps from black holes, giving way to alliances, trade and wars.
 
Based on observations made with space drones on different planets, stars and planetary ships, where humans,humanoids, aliens, mongrels, robots and entities interact and die...
